rows.label: qst701110_msg0001
rows.name:
Fufufu, from the looks of it,
it seems to have gone well.

rows.label: qst701110_msg0002
rows.name:
How about it, young lady? Have you
found what you want to accomplish?

rows.label: qst701110_msg0003
rows.name:
Not yet... I don't really know.
But I'm thinking about it.

rows.label: qst701110_msg0004
rows.name:
Until now, I've been so busy just
trying to get by, I haven't really
thought about my own goals.

rows.label: qst701110_msg0005
rows.name:
I see. But there's no
need to be ashamed.

rows.label: qst701110_msg0006
rows.name:
No matter what the world is like,
always be "yourself." If you have
a core, you can live flexibly.

rows.label: qst701110_msg0007
rows.name:
That philosophy... has something in common
with water. Like how the soft and weak
can overcome the hard and strong...

rows.label: qst701110_msg0008
rows.name:
Hmmm, you really do have an
interesting way of thinking. How
about we have a long talk sometime?

rows.label: qst701110_msg0011
rows.name:
You are not a machine that
just fulfills its mission.
You must live as you please.

rows.label: qst701110_msg0012
rows.name:
That's right, Wadatsumi. His
Majesty has me, after all.

rows.label: qst701110_msg0014
rows.name:
Your name is Wadatsumi, is it? Can't
I be your tea-drinking friend?
